{"tid":2164872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入數入唔到五百蚊紙⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:56:48.000Z","uid":324251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce607016fbe00c4207ff56dbcfa8d8b20346e6f8","tid":2164872,"uid":324251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"今日去匯豐入錢，入左700蚊<br />\n兩張紅色一張啡色<br />\n佢淨係食左紅色啡色嘔翻出黎<br />\n我拎翻睇原來中銀嘅<br />\n以為自己嗰張係偽鈔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持實驗精神我去左中銀櫃員機gum錢<br />\n正常銀聯嘅卡應該撳到（不過要收手續費）<br />\n但今日一入卡就話唔接受貴卡<br />\n<br />\n姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪中資比外資制裁左"},{"pid":"32415e1df7853ab8be20162e7166657834b18a86","tid":2164872,"uid":281189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"似係你被人制裁緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569aa9d2c33dc74283671482fd0b963c3601567b","tid":2164872,"uid":324251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32415e1df7853ab8be20162e7166657834b18a86","tid":2164872,"uid":281189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"似係你被人制裁緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我洗左張500蚊又得喎"}]}